{{What were the challenges:}}
Before starting to work on ShopiCSV I hadn't worked a so much with JavaScript and {{React}}, same goes with Auth0, {{AWS}}, internationalization and proper {{CI/CD}}.
Thankfully, I was able to use my {{extensive experience}} with software engineering and {{project management}} to bring this project to where it is today and I intend to {{continue}} working on this project in order to make it available to {{Shopify merchants}} needing it.
